name: Leap up no Justu: Double
description:
Leap up no jutsu: Double is the next version of the game Leap up no Jutsu. From now on, you must control two characters to avoid obstacles at the same time by clicking on the side where the character needs to jump. By collecting gold coins along the way, you can go to the store to buy new character skins and backgrounds - giving you more inspiration while playing. Hope you enjoy your time playing the game.
